Package: glymotif
Title: Extract glycan motifs from glycan structures
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Bin", "Fu", , "23110220018@m.fudan.edu.cn", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-8567-2997"))
Description: 
    This package extracts glycan motifs (substructures) from glycan structures. 
    It uses `glyparse` to parse glycan structures text representations and
    uses `glyrepr` to analyze glycan structure graphs.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
